Package jminusminus

Class CLConstantPool

  • java.lang.Object
    • jminusminus.CLConstantPool
  • class CLConstantPool
extends java.lang.Object
    Representation of a class' constant_pool table (JVM Spec Section 4.5). An instance of CLConstantPool is created when a class is read using CLAbsorber or constructed using CLEmitter.

    • Constructor Summary
